The paper focuses on face detection, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method also involves machine learning techniques, such as neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the running efficiency on different hardware platforms, which is related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM).
